This module extends the functionality of 'Warehouse Management' to show
you the stock availability (Free To Use Quantity) of each product as
part of its name in the product drop-down widget on stock picking.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

To use this module, you need to:

1. Go to *Inventory > Operations > Transfers* and edit a stock picking
   or create a new one.
2. Add a new stock picking line (Operations) and click on the product
   field to see the available products to select.
3. You will see the stock availability (Free To Use Quantity) of each
   product as part of its name.

